        "subject": "LU-18797 build: Multiple kmod-lustre-client RPMs for different kernels",
        "message": "LU-18797 build: Multiple kmod-lustre-client RPMs for different kernels\n\nAllow installation of multiple kmod-lustre-client RPMs for different\nkernel versions without file conflicts.\n\n- Rename ChangeLog-lustre to include the build version\n  (e.g., ChangeLog-lustre-<version>)\n- Remove the redundant COPYING file from the kmod package since\n  license info is already included in the modules.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\n\nSigned-off-by: Chakshu Kansal <ckansal@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I9f3788dd342e009a77f2bab382a787d73e1e0483\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/61832\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nReviewed-by: Shaun Tancheff <shaun.tancheff@hpe.com>\n"
      },
